Review.Contenu: A purchase of several pieces of equipment was made and they sent others, they had to be bought elsewhere, when requesting the refund of the money they say that in 3 days and I have been waiting for more than 2 months for the refund of what was paid.Se realizo una  compra  de varios equipos y enviaron otros, hubo que comprarlos en otro sitio, al momento de solicitar la devolución del dinero dicen que  en 3 días y llevo mas de 2 meses esperando el reintegro de lo pagado.
